# VitalSync — Next Steps Roadmap

A prioritized learning + implementation plan covering Redis caching, chatbot evaluation & improvements, AWS Bedrock migration with credit management, and LLM evaluation frameworks.

---

## Current State Summary

| Area | Status |
|------|--------|
| **Redis** | **[IN PROGRESS]** Connected via ioredis. Central `cacheService` built with granular `invalidateSpecific` logic. |
| **AI Chatbot** | ReAct agent loop with Gemini 2.5 Flash, 4 tools, memory extraction, Helicone observability. Uses `@google/generative-ai` SDK directly. |
| **Dashboard** | **[IN PROGRESS]** Metrics Service (Weight/Habits/Streaks) now uses cache-aside pattern. Workouts and Nutrition pending. |
| **LLM Eval** | No evaluation framework, no test suite, no guardrails beyond max-agent-turns cap. |
| **Credits/Billing** | No concept of per-user usage tracking or credit management. |

